      <title>南非将于 2 月公布私营铁路投资规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/south-africa-to-unveil-private-rail-investment-rules-by-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非交通部长芭芭拉·克里西表示，南非计划在六个月内完成私营企业使用国有港口和铁路基础设施的框架，此举可能有助于政府解决影响经济增长的严重物流限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/south-africa-to-unveil-private-rail-investment-rules-by-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
